Why AGPL-3.0

FaithFilter is released under the AGPL so it stays free and open for every
family, school and community that wants to run it — and so that anyone who
offers it as a hosted service must share their improvements back. The
copyright holder may additionally offer the software under separate terms
(for example, to operate a hosted version); the AGPL applies to this public
